      <title>克罗地亚将于四月投票，执政党吹捧欧元和工资上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/croatia-to-vote-in-april-as-ruling-party-touts-euro-wage-hikes</link>
